    %h1.block-title Accessing the middleman development server within your network
    %article.view-mode-full.content
      %p
        Depending on the server settings, you should be able to see the source at
        %code http://localhost:4567/
        or
        %code http://0.0.0.0:4567/
      %p To access this domain from another device like a tablet or smartphone, you need to be connected on the same network as the middleman development server. Now find out what your IP address is. The easiest to work with is a fixed IP address.
      %p
        If your IP address is for example
        %code 192.168.0.1
        then you can find your site at
        %code http://192.168.0.1.xip.io:4567
      %p xip.io is a magic domain name that provides wildcard DNS. xip.io runs a custom DNS server on the public Internet. When your computer looks up a xip.io domain, the xip.io DNS server extracts the IP address from the domain and sends it back in the response.

